creator: Joyce Kilmer
description:
LibriVox recording of Main Street, and Other Poems by Joyce Kilmer.
Read in English by Sonia; Urban Bard; Newgatenovelist; Ryan Fry; Greg Giordano; BettyB; VolcanoPukebag; JudyDerby; Jacquelyn Bengfort
This is a book of poems by Joyce Kilmer. It includes several of his religious poems and poems about World War I, in which the author himself lost his life in 1918. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
